name: COVID19SNOMEDValueSetForPregnancyComplications
title: COVID19 SNOMED Value Set for Pregnancy Complications
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains terms related to conditions complicating pregnancy.),(Data Element Scope: ),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes conditions complicating pregnancy (e.g., Pre-existing essential hypertension complicating pregnancy) and complications due to pregnancy (e.g., Pre-eclampsia).),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes terms related to labor, delivery and postpartum states.)
